<i>noun</i>: 작별 [작뼐], 이탈 [이ː탈], 이산 [이ː산], 이별 [이ː별], 생이별 [생니별], 분립 [불립], 분리 [불리], 결별 [결별], 가름 [가름] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>작별 [작뼐]</dt><br>
<dd>farewell; parting; separation</dd><br>
<dd>서로 인사를 나누고 헤어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of exchanging good-byes and parting with each other.</dd><br>
<dt>이탈 [이ː탈]</dt><br>
<dd>breakaway; separation; secession</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 범위나 줄, 기준 등에서 떨어져 나오거나 떨어져 나감.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of getting out of a certain range or deviating from a line, standard, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>이산 [이ː산]</dt><br>
<dd>separation; dispersion</dd><br>
<dd>헤어지거나 이별하여 흩어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being dispersed due to a parting or separation.</dd><br>
<dt>이별 [이ː별]</dt><br>
<dd>parting; separation; farewell</dd><br>
<dd>오랫동안 만나지 못하게 떨어져 있거나 헤어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of separating or parting from someone so that one cannot see him/her for a long time.</dd><br>
<dt>생이별 [생니별]</dt><br>
<dd>separation; parting</dd><br>
<dd>어쩔 수 없는 사정으로 부부, 부모와 자식, 형제끼리 따로 떨어지게 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>A separation of husband and wife, parents and children, brothers and sisters due to unavoidable circumstances.</dd><br>
<dt>분립 [불립]</dt><br>
<dd>separation; schism</dd><br>
<dd>갈라져서 따로 자리함. 또는 나누어서 자리하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>Things being divided and separately established; the process of dividing and separately establishing things.</dd><br>
<dt>분리 [불리]</dt><br>
<dd>separation</dd><br>
<dd>서로 나뉘어 떨어짐. 또는 그렇게 되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being divided and separated; the act of dividing and separating things.</dd><br>
<dt>결별 [결별]</dt><br>
<dd>separation; breakup; split</dd><br>
<dd>관계나 사귐을 끊고 헤어지는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Ending a relationship and parting.</dd><br>
<dt>가름 [가름]</dt><br>
<dd>1. separation; division</dd><br>
<dd>서로 나누어 따로따로 되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of dividing something into separate parts.</dd><br>
<dd>2. distinguishing; separation</dd><br>
<dd>차이를 구별하거나 구분함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of distinguishing the difference between people or things.</dd><br>
<dd>3. judgment; determination</dd><br>
<dd>어느 한 쪽이 더 낫거나 옳다고 판별하거나 결정함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of judging or deciding that either one of two sides is better or right.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>